eu.amidst.dynamic.variables

Class DynamicVariables

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.amidst.dynamic.variables.DynamicVariables
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Iterable<Variable>

    public class DynamicVariables
extends Object
implements Iterable<Variable>, Serializable
    The DynamicVariables class defines and handles the operations related to the set of variables of a DynamicBayesianNetwork model.
